    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Card game for two or more persons in which the players bet on the value of the card in their hands, the winner taking the pool. There are many variations.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000046684/Random House Unabridged Dictionary (1993)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指稱提供給兩位以上玩家參與的紙牌遊戲，玩家根據拿到牌的點數大小下注，贏家可拿走全部賭注，有多種不同玩法。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
